# PigeonHouse Protocol — Cursor Rules

You are working with PigeonHouse, a deflationary token launchpad on Solana.

## Key Facts
- Program: `BV1RxkAaD5DjXMsnofkVikFUUYdrDg1v8YgsQ3iyDNoL` (Anchor, Token-2022)
- All tokens are Token-2022 with MetadataPointer extension (6 decimals)
- Bonding curve: constant product AMM (x * y = k)
- Quote assets: PIGEON, SOL (wSOL), SKR
- Fee: 2% per trade (1.5% burn/reserve + 0.5% treasury)
- Graduation: auto-migrate to Raydium CPMM with locked LP

## Token Addresses
- PIGEON: `4fSWEw2wbYEUCcMtitzmeGUfqinoafXxkhqZrA9Gpump` (Token-2022)
- SOL: `So11111111111111111111111111111111111111112` (SPL Token)
- SKR: `SKRbvo6Gf7GondiT3BbTfuRDPqLWei4j2Qy2NPGZhW3` (SPL Token)

## PDAs
- GlobalConfig: `["pigeon_house_config"]`
- BondingCurve: `["bonding_curve", token_mint]`
- FeeVault: `["fee_vault"]`
- QuoteAssetConfig: `["quote_asset", quote_mint]`

## API Endpoints
- `GET /api/platform` — all tokens
- `GET /api/token/{mint}` — bonding curve state
- `GET /api/trades/{mint}` — recent trades
- `GET /api/leaderboard` — creator leaderboard
- `GET /api/prices` — PIGEON/SOL prices

## Important
- Use TOKEN_2022_PROGRAM_ID for PIGEON and all PigeonHouse tokens
- Use TOKEN_PROGRAM_ID for SOL (wSOL) and SKR
- ATAs owned by bonding_curve PDA must use `allowOwnerOffCurve: true`
- IDL: https://941pigeon.fun/idl/pigeon_house.json
- Referrer goes in remaining_accounts[0] for fee share

## MCP Server
For live data queries, use the PigeonHouse MCP server:
```json
{ "mcpServers": { "pigeonhouse": { "command": "npx", "args": ["pigeonhouse-mcp"] } } }
```
